    "answers": [
        {
            "owner": {
                "profile_image": "https://i.sstatic.net/irQpr.jpg?s=256",
                "account_id": 2814779,
                "user_type": "registered",
                "user_id": 2420301,
                "link": "https://stackoverflow.com/users/2420301/marc-balmer",
                "reputation": 1830,
                "display_name": "Marc Balmer"
            },
            "content_license": "CC BY-SA 3.0",
            "score": 1,
            "is_accepted": false,
            "last_activity_date": 1408266338,
            "creation_date": 1408266338,
            "body": "<p>So I solved this problem.  It is not enough to set the line spacing to 24 dots using ESC '3' 24, but you have to print the image in page mode.<\/p>\n\n<p>To enter page mode:  ESC 'L'<\/p>\n\n<p>Then you have to set the image area using ESC 'W', here I do it in C:<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>           h2 = h * 2 + 30;\n            /* Set the printing area, h * 2 because of double density */\n            seq[0] = 0x1b;\n            seq[1] = 'W';\n            seq[2] = 0;     /* xl */\n            seq[3] = 0;     /* xh */\n            seq[4] = 0;     /* yl */\n            seq[5] = 0;     /* yh */\n            seq[6] = 0;     /* dxl */\n            seq[7] = 2;     /* dxh */\n            seq[8] = h2 % 256;      /* dyl */\n            seq[9] = h2 / 256;      /* dyh */\n            if (write(fd, seq, 10) != 10)\n                    goto finish;\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>Now send the image data and finally print with sending 0x0c, this also returns the printer to standard mode.<\/p>\n\n<p>By using page mode, the white stripes on the image went away.<\/p>\n\n<p>BTW, this seems to be an oddity of EPSON TM-T88 printers, I neither see these white lines on the TM-T500A nor on e.g. Aures printers.  On these printers I can use standard mode to print images.<\/p>\n",
            "answer_id": 25347790,
            "question_id": 21192888
        },
        {
            "owner": {
                "profile_image": "https://i.sstatic.net/QXR8z.jpg?s=256",
                "account_id": 4496800,
                "user_type": "registered",
                "user_id": 3656419,
                "link": "https://stackoverflow.com/users/3656419/zeroworks",
